name: PurdueFood
0:
”Alexa, ask Purdue Food what's for breakfast at Ford today”
”Alexa, ask Purdue Food what is at Wiley for lunch on Wednesday”
”Alexa, ask Purdue Food what is dinner tomorrow at Earhart”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: purdue food
des:
Hungry and want to know whats for breakfast, lunch, or dinner at your favorite dining court? How about tomorrow, Friday, or next Wednesday?

Purdue Food is here to help. Simply provide the meal, day, and dining court you'd like to hear about and Alexa will read you your options.

Meals: Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner
Dining Courts: Ford, Wiley, Earhart, Hillenbrand, Windsor
Day: Any day of the week, including "Today" and "Tomorrow"

--DEV SUPPORT--
This was developed by a Computer Science Student at Purdue University. While studies come first, I am dedicated to improving Purdue Food to the best of my ability.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
